Zainab Balogun-Nwachukwu (amụrụ 10 Ọktoba 1989) bụ onye na- eme ihe nkiri, ihe nlereanya na onye na-egosi ihe onyonyo na Naịjirịa
Ọ malitere ịme ngosi mgbe ọ dị obere mgbe agụrụ ya afọ 16
Apụtala ya n'ọtụtụ mkpọsa mba ụwa maka ụdị dị iche iche
O jikọrọ aka wee tọọ ntọala J-ist TV, usoro ihe nkiri ịntanetị nke na-egosipụta ọdịbendị Afrịka na ọtụtụ isiokwu dị iche iche; usoro a nwere ajụjụ ọnụ nke metụtara ụfọdụ ndị ama ama n'Africa
Balogun na-arụ ọrụ dị ka onye na- egosi ihe na onyonyo maka EbonyLife TV, ụlọ ọrụ ebe igwe onyonyo nke ọ na-akwado ugbu a ma na-emepụta The Spot , ihe ngosi okwu  nke ọwa, ya na Lamide Akintobi
Balogun na -egosikwa dị ka onye na -emeputa ihe na onye so na -emepụta ihe na Jumia TV, ihe ngosi teleshopping.
A mụrụ Balogun na London nye nne na nna Naịjirịa,   ebe a zụlitere ya na nnukwu ezinụlọ, ọkachasị na Clapham, mpaghara South West London
Ọ bụ onye Egba, na -ekwukwa na ọ sitere na ezinụlọ si Abeokuta, Ogun State
N'ihi ụdị ọrụ nne ya na -arụ, ọ kwagara ọtụtụ ebe ma jiri ọtụtụ afọ ndụ ya tolite ya na ndị ikwu
Enwetara agụmakwụkwọ ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ya na Sacred Heart RC Secondary School
Mmasị ya na nka bidoro site na ya na -ekere òkè mgbe niile na ihe ngosi nka na egwuregwu ụlọ akwụkwọ
Ọ mụrụ egwu wee mechaa sonye n'òtù ukwe ụlọ akwụkwọ ma mesịa mebe otu ụmụ agbọghọ R&B na ndị enyi abụọ akpọrọ Regné (akpọrọ "ọchịchị")
Ọ gara Christ the King Sixth Form College ebe ọ gụchara A Levels na Law, Psychology, na English Language & Literature
Ọ gara mahadum Kent na Medway ebe ọ nwetara nzere bachelọ nke iwu (LLB)
Balogun rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye nlereanya mgbe Premier Models Management nyochachara ya mgbe ọ dị afọ 16
Mgbe ọ nwetasịrị asambodo iwu ya, ọ malitere ịpụta n'ihe ngosi dịka BBC One 's Girl Girl, ihe nkiri Bollywood Cocktail (2012), na The Charlatans nke Ashley Waters dere
N'oge na -adịghị anya ọ hụrụ onwe ya na onye ntụzi akụkọ ámá ámá Christopher Nolan na 2011 maka ihe nkiri The Dark Knight Rises, nke ọ kọwara dị ka "ahụmịhe a na -agaghị echefu echefu"
Balogun bụ onye na -egosi ihe onyonyo ugbu a, onye na -emepụta ma na -egosi ihe nkiri maka EbonyLife TV, netwọk igwe onyonyo nke ntụrụndụ
Ọ mepụtala ihe ngosi dịka EL Ugbu a, ihe ngosi akụkọ ntụrụndụ kwa ụbọchị maka ndị kachasị ọhụrụ na ejiji, egwu na nka
Ebuka Obi-Uchendu na Lamide Akintobi na-esonyere ya ugbu a na The Spot, ihe ngosi a na-eme kwa ụbọchị
Na Mee 2018 Balogun lụrụ Dikko Nwachukwu, onye guzobere Jetwest Airways
Di na nwunye ahụ lụrụ alụmdi na nwunye nke omenala na 13 Mee na Lagos, Nigeria.
Balogun kewara oge ya n'etiti London, England, na Lagos, Nigeria.
